  wait_for_input
  animate jen normal_smile
end

tab: [indignant] Oh, I'm sure. He remains in the Kill category.

tab: [asking] Boss, your go. And since we're doing people in high places...

tab: [asking] Kiss, Marry, Kill. Chief Anderson, Patricia Becker with the Heraldic -

mordecai: [proud] Nice!

tab: [explain] - and Tristan, that guy from City Hall!

if has_joseph
  joseph: [smile] Who's it going to be?
else
  jen: [pointing_smile] Who's it gonna' be?
end
animate tab normal

unset kmk_chief
unset kmk_patricia
unset kmk_tristan

choose
* Hmm, I'll be kissing Chief Anderson. Aggressively.
  kmk_chief = "kiss"
  hide_bubbles
