* [not kmk_patricia] I'll marry Patricia Becker. Maybe improve our press coverage.
  kmk_patricia = "marry"
  hide_bubbles
  animate jen normal_smile
  animate tab normal
  animate mordecai proud
  jen_approval +5

* [not kmk_tristan] Marry Tristan. That boy has a bright political future.
  kmk_tristan = "marry"
  hide_bubbles
  animate jen normal_smile
  animate tab laugh
  animate mordecai proud
  tab_approval +5
end

choose
* [not kmk_chief] ...And unfortunately kill the Chief. By elimination of the other options.
  kmk_chief = "kill"
  hide_bubbles
  animate jen normal_smile
  animate tab normal
  animate mordecai proud
  tab_approval -5

* [not kmk_patricia] ...And unfortunately kill miss Becker. By elimination of the other options.
  kmk_patricia = "kill"
  hide_bubbles
  animate jen normal_smile
  animate tab laugh
  animate mordecai normal
  mordecai_approval -5

* [not kmk_tristan] ...And unfortunately kill Tristan. By elimination of the other options.
  kmk_tristan = "kill"
  hide_bubbles
  animate jen normal_smile
  animate tab laugh
  animate mordecai proud
